to acquire Intermedia Communications Inc. Intermedia, based in
Tampa, Fla., is one of the biggest independent operators of voice
and data networks in the country. Intermedia's controlling stake in
Digex, a leading operator of computer centers that run Web sites,
is also part of the deal.
</P>
